\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Was there any announcement in the paper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No, nothing like - no, we didn't do that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did your parents treat you both any differently once you were engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. Treat us both the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 How did you choose your wedding ring did you have a wedding ring as well?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes. Yes. We had that in the same shop. When I - you get this - I don't know, you get this little present with that one. I forg
et what it was now. A - a butter knife and - dish I think, silver butter knife and dish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Who gave you this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 The - the - jeweller, when he bought - when he bought the wedding ring, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Was that often the case?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Well they do, I thi
nk they do give you a present, 'cos we had a - we had the engagement ring there see, and a wedding ring, see, and - and then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 So you were a good customer really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, yes, that's right, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you save up very much before getting married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Oh I saved up all we could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you find a house before you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes. Up at Lanscove we had a - we went right in there, married in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you know it was coming up before you got married, did you know that there was a chance of a house there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 
Well they were empty and they'd been empty for a long long time. So when we knew we were getting married I - I approached the - well they belonged to a bank really 'cos I think the builder went bankrupt or something an
d I had to pay my rent to the bank in Plymouth. So the bank they didn't trouble anything about it, they just said, yes, have it, and there you are.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Have you had any rings since marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Eternity rings or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. No, I didn't want one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you ever exchange any other love tokens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you buy any household equipment before you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Oh yes, I used to - when I used to get me wages I used to - put away what I could and get little things, dif
ferent little things - and keep them. Bedding and things like that. I got a good bit of that before I was married, 'cos you could get it cheaper then you see. I mean ten shillings would go a long way, what - well, further than a pound would go today.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you have a bottom drawer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, what I had, a bottom drawer, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Would you have that in the Morrows or at Tidwell?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 I used to take it home to mother. And she used to take carre of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did your parents help you at all in setting up a home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 
Well they couldn't very well. They hadn't got much money to do that. They'd be - give us our wedding reception. But - as regards anything else we had to fight for ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Who did you first see to arrange the wedding, was it a Vicar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, the Vicar. Because we couldn't get married at the chapel then, - it wasn't licen}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1315105\charrsid1131893 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 ed. The Vicar - Reverend Chamberlain. Nice old chap he was too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 That's the chap who came down to help look after your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No, no, that was Mr Smith. Before Mr Chamberlain came.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Mr Smith died did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Oh yes, died of cancer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 How long was it before the wedding that you went to see the Vicar to sort things out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Three weeks, 'cos we had to have - the banns had to be called three weeks you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 What day did you get married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Eleventh of - on A Saturday. 12th of November.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Was there any particular reason for choosing the wedding day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. No only Saturday you see they - they could get off easier Saturdays.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Why did you choose a religious ceremony?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 
Oh well I - I don't think 'tis marriage without you are married in church or chapel, I - I don't reckon the - the - what do you call it, offices - Registrars - I don't like those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 You didn't have any difficulty getting your parents agreement?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. Not at all. Not at all. They did all they could to help us then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you want a large or a small wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Oh well I - I had a - I had a lot of friends - come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Where would they come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Around - around, you know, our friends around here, and - of course my sister was living at - Bayside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Where's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Down - Staveton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Was she in service there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, service there, yes. She was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 With a Doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No, no, no. Gentry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 How did you decide who to invite to the wedding, did you divide it up between relatives and neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Well we just - we just invite - well I had to do that, my husband wouldn't have nothing, to do with that, I had to do it all. His side 
and my side you see. I expect there was between twenty and thirty there with - with our friends as well. Because he's got a lot of - he had a lot of relatives you see, sisters and brothers. And one brother but a lot of sisters. All came, yes, yes they all
 came.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you send the invites by word of mouth or by card?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 I sent - I sent a letter to one of 'em and told 'em to tell the others because they was all in Bovey you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 You think it was about evenly divided between his people and your people?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did anybody have to stay overnight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. We hadn't got the room if they did. They all went back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 What time was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Oh the wedding was twelve o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 So that they had time to get down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 They had time to get down, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Would they come in horse and traps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 
No, they had - they had motor cars then. Yes. Taxis. In they days. Yes, they had taxis. In fact we used one of the taxis for the wedding. We hadn't far to go but he - they made us go -
 made us go up in a - I didn't want to go up in a car but they made me go up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Just you on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes. Me and me - me and me father and - and me sister, she was bridesmaid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did your husband go by car as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, he went up first. Of course. And the best man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Who was the best man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 My brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 How were the costs of the wedding met, did your parents pay for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, they paid - for it. Yes they paid for it. Well we - see we used - I told you we used to salt in 
a pig, well we had a lovely - lovely piece of ham to boil you see. And - father went up Buckfastleigh and got a great rib of beef. We had a good do I can tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Everyone came piling back for the reception did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Where did you have the reception?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 
Home. Home. We had a great big table in the sitting room, 'cos it was - it 'tis a great big room the sitting room is. Had a great big table in the sitting room and then we served from the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you do anything special the last week before the wedding like a hen party or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. No, nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 What happened on your last day at work, did anything special happen with the Morrows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. No. They gave me the present - gave me a nice present an
d - wished me well because I mean I - I used to see 'em a lot after that you see, the Morrows. When I used to go to Buckfastleigh I used to often pop in there. 'Cos he was our doctor you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 What did you get as a going away present from the Morrows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Oh a lovely pair of blankets. Oh ah. Lovely. -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 You didn't go back to the Morrows after you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Oh no, only - only visited 'em. That was all. Oh yes, he used to like to see me come in, I - it was like home I mean I - I didn't have 
to knock or anything, I used to just go in you see. After I'd been in the surgery I'd go in and see 'em and my mother used to too. They treated my mother very nice, Doctor Morrow did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did your husband see you on the wedding day before the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 
Yes, he - he - as a matter of fact he did 'cos he had to sleep there. He - he lost his way coming, I thought he wasn't going to turn up. He lost his way. Yes.
