\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, I had it all on a - table back - back in the back of the room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did anybody make speeches at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No, I don't think they did then. I don't think they did - I don't think - I know - I don't think - I'm sure my husband wouldn't do it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 What about the best man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No, he didn't - he didn't make - they didn't do it then. That's only recently that that has come out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you have any special seating arrangement at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Oh yes. Yes, we sat - we - we - my husband and I sat at the top of the table and my mother and father next
 to me. And then the rest - the guests come in, the bridesmaid and - and - the nearest relatives then came next to us down the table. Yes, that's right, that's right. That's right, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Was there any dancing or singing afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, they - yes, they had a bit of dancing and singing - we had a - a gram}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1315105\charrsid1131893 o}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 phone. And - we played that and had a - a sing-song and - and those who could dance danced. I never danced, I could never dance. Oh yes, we had a - I tell you it was a lovely - lovely time.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 How long did it go on for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 
Yes, we were late, eleven o'clock I expect. Then they had to get back to Bovey after that. My father - my husband's father and mother and - and all - all the Bovey people. Had to get back to Bovey.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 How would they get back, in cars?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 
Well the cars stopped you see, we - we - well we - we give them their meals you see and they came in our place. So - we were all - I mean - weren't - we didn't even rent the car, they come in - come in with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 These were hired cars?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes, hired cars. Yes, hired cars, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you go away on a honeymoon at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Were there any practical jokes played on you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. They tried it but I caught 'em. I don't know what they was goin
g to do. His mother - she went upstairs and - and she didn't know I was in the room, she said, which room - which room are they going to sleep in? I thought, all right. Oh, her said, I didn't know you was here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did you stay at your mother's house that first night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Or did you go straight into your own house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No, no, we stayed - we stayed there that night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Did your husband carry you over the threshold?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No, good gracious me no. I wouldn't have done it if he'd wanted to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Do you remember attending any other weddings when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 No. Not when I was young no. I was grown up - when my brother was married, yes. Ruth was two year old then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009454 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Do you remember anything like a funeral while you were living at the Doctor's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8653130 ER  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7353437\charrsid1131893 Not at that time, no. No. No, no. No.
\par }}